sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Flask-RESTX API
    participant DB as SQLite Database

    User->>Frontend: Enter email and username
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/v1/auth/register
    API->>API: Validate email and username
    API->>DB: Create User
    API->>DB: Create PlayerProfile
    DB-->>API: User and profile saved
    API-->>Frontend: Return success response
    Frontend-->>User: Redirect to profile or play page